Package: lithicscarpattern
Title: Lithic Flaking Scar Orientation Alignment and Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Author", "Name", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for aligning and analysing 3-D lithic flaking scar
    orientation data. Implements two alignment pipelines (SVD-based and
    Lin 2024), plane-deviation diagnostics, circular-statistics descriptors
    (Mean Resultant Length R, Elongation E, Isotropy I), and Plotly-based
    interactive 3-D visualisations.
